<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>MediCare+ - 스마트 병원 예약 및 업무 관리 시스템</title>
  <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
  <script src="https://unpkg.com/feather-icons"></script>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css"> </head>
<body class="min-h-screen flex flex-col items-center justify-center p-6 relative">
  
  {{> components/header}}
  {{> components/sidebar}}

  <div class="text-center mb-12">
    <div class="w-20 h-20 bg-indigo-600 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center text-white mx-auto mb-6 shadow-lg">
      <i data-feather="activity" class="w-10 h-10"></i>
    </div>
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-slate-800 mb-4">MediCare+</h1>
    <p class="text-lg text-slate-500">스마트 병원 예약 및 업무 관리 시스템</p>
  </div>

  <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 w-full max-w-3xl">
    <button
      onclick="location.href='/patient'"
      class="bg-white p-10 rounded-3xl shadow-sm border border-slate-200 hover:shadow-md hover:border-indigo-300 transition-all group flex flex-col items-center text-center z-10"
    >
      <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-indigo-50 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-indigo-600 mb-6 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">
        <i data-feather="user" class="w-8 h-8"></i>
      </div>
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-800 mb-2">환자용</h2>
      <p class="text-slate-500">진료 예약 및 확인</p>
    </button>

    <button
      onclick="location.href='/login'"
      class="bg-white p-10 rounded-3xl shadow-sm border border-slate-200 hover:shadow-md hover:border-indigo-300 transition-all group flex flex-col items-center text-center z-10"
    >
      <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-slate-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-slate-600 mb-6 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">
        <i data-feather="shield" class="w-8 h-8"></i>
      </div>
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-800 mb-2">직원용</h2>
      <p class="text-slate-500">업무 시스템 로그인</p>
    </button>
  </div>

  {{> components/footer}}
  
  <script>
    document.addEventListener("DOMContentLoaded", () => {
      feather.replace();
    });
  </script>
</body>
</html>